import org.apache.spark.ml.Pipeline
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature._
import org.apache.spark.sql.SQLContext
import org.apache.spark.storage.StorageLevel

import org.apache.spark.ml.classification.{NaiveBayes}
import org.apache.spark.ml.evaluation.MulticlassClassificationEvaluator
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature._

  //  val categoryToArticleMappingDF = sc.textFile("hdfs://172.26.5.36/analytics/wiki/mapping/*", 1000)
  val categoryToArticleMappingDF = sc.textFile("file:///home/ipertushin/IdeaProjects/pornocluster/data/wiki/mapping-en/*",100)
        .map { s =>
                """\(([A-Za-z\s\d]{3,60}),\[(.*)\]\)""".r.findFirstMatchIn(s) match {
                  case Some(m) => {
                    (m.group(1), m.group(2).split(", ").toSeq)
        
                  }
                  case None => ("Unknown", Seq.empty[String])
                }
        }
        .toDF("category", "terms")
        .persist(StorageLevel.DISK_ONLY) 
        
    val categories = categoryToArticleMappingDF
        .select("category")
        .registerTempTable("WikiCategories")
     
      
    // Index labels, adding metadata to the label column.
    // Fit on whole dataset to include all labels in index.
    val labelIndexer = new StringIndexer()
      .setInputCol("category")
      .setOutputCol("indexedLabel")
      .fit(categoryToArticleMappingDF)
      

    val hashingTF = new HashingTF()
      .setNumFeatures(1000)
      .setInputCol("terms")
      .setOutputCol("tfFeatures")

    val idf = new IDF()
      .setInputCol("tfFeatures")
      .setOutputCol("tfidfFeatures")

    val normalizer = new Normalizer()
      .setInputCol("tfidfFeatures")
      .setOutputCol("normalizedFeatures")


     val scaler = new StandardScaler()
      .setInputCol("normalizedFeatures")
      .setOutputCol("scaledFeatures")
   
     val nb = new NaiveBayes()
     nb.setLabelCol("indexedLabel")
     nb.setFeaturesCol("scaledFeatures")

  
    // Convert indexed labels back to original labels.
    val labelConverter = new IndexToString()
      .setInputCol("prediction")
      .setOutputCol("predictedLabel")
      .setLabels(labelIndexer.labels)

    val pipeline = new Pipeline()
      .setStages(Array(
        labelIndexer,
        hashingTF,
        idf,
        normalizer,
        scaler,
        nb,
        labelConverter)
      )
      
    // Train model
    val model = pipeline.fit(categoryToArticleMappingDF)
    
    //val pathToPdmlData = "hdfs://172.26.5.36/analytics/packets-html-langs/en"
    val pathToPdmlData = "file:///home/ipertushin/IdeaProjects/pornocluster/data/pdml-eng/*"
    
    val pdmlDataTermsDF =  sc.textFile(pathToPdmlData,100)
        .filter{s => !s.isEmpty()}
        .map(s => (s.hashCode, s.split(", ")))
        .toDF("id", "terms")
    
    // Make predictions 
    model.transform(pdmlDataTermsDF)
         .registerTempTable("ResultPredictions")
